Dear |receiver.fullname|,

I wish to raise a concern about the new tenant on my floor. There have been some strange goings-on since they moved in, strangers and odd sounds at all hours.
Could you please keep an eye on them? I'm worried for my safety.

Respectfully yours,
|fullname|
|firstname|,\r\nYou know I am too busy to worry about 'strange sounds' and the like. Please don't bother me with this again
